{"tid":2066618,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"踢爆律政司司長鄭若驊係私人檢控(的士撞人案)的部署同黨棍梁卓然的部署","createTime":"2020-06-16T11:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T14:26:38.000Z","uid":26770,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"98fd39b7a9a22b02ea4cbce5d55e8049bc388ddc","tid":2066618,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:35:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200616/POCL62I5TDN6PXNOTWCITLFCZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200616%2FPOCL62I5TDN6PXNOTWCITLFCZ4%2F&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa4%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=20749c9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200616%2FPOCL62I5TDN6PXNOTWCITLFCZ4%2F&h=42cd095b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200616/POCL62I5TDN6PXNOTWCITLFCZ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n她繼而指，提出私人檢控的權利是普通法制度下重要的一環，但有關權利有機會遭人濫用，「我們不應容忍有人提出毫無事實根據甚至瑣碎無聊的私人檢控，或可能懷有不恰當動機或基於政治因素而提出私人檢控」，其後搬出《基本法》第63條，指律政司有憲制責任主管刑事檢控，若認為私人檢控「沒有合理定罪機會、違反公衆利益、基於不恰當動機而提出或構成濫用程序等」，有責任介入並停止相關的法律程序，<ins>律政司亦有責任邀請法庭行使酌情權，擱置構成濫用程序的聆訊。</ins><br />\n<br />\n1 呢個講法其實係迫香港法官主動踢case<br />\n已有法官向路透講中方人員經常要脅要點點點判<ins>,用釋法威脅法官就範</ins><br />\n因為私人檢控涉及的士司機鄭國泉發動恐怖襲擊,受害人終生殘廢<br />\n邊個踢case就等於恐怖活動共犯<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊想迫法院攬上身自己就脫身<br />\n香港法律界好興你叫國安法,我就lesser evil支持23條<br />\n<br />\n2再一次證明我對刑事檢控專員豬狗不如梁卓然的指控係堅<br />\n正係呢條友堅持要屈到荃灣警局輪姦案受害人坐監去滅聲<br />\n呢條友係律政司的黨委書記及香港東廠廠公<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2066163/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2066163/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>好簡單,大家做野有厭惡性都一定會踢比手下,特別呢類有機坐監的野</ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解刑事檢控專員豬狗不如梁卓然次次可以縮係安全的大後方, doj邊個真正話事係好明顯</span>"},{"pid":"ea23fe1cec25e6254a59dabd76c43f6210ffaf37","tid":2066618,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75222dea673762878661dceac61ec9025c212da","tid":2066618,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48266944aa560b87fb82efcf2fcece4ee5fcbdf4","tid":2066618,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417b489b642fd214a52412d9a688cb76fba490b6","tid":2066618,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f712fd3b61fcd9afdece106484b4863485fe0147","tid":2066618,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8a5ec48281de09e4e8e89d5484386248276dc7","tid":2066618,"uid":76609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:42:05.000Z","msg":"整多幾人單私人檢控，<br />\n等佢求其撤到一單就當有做野，<br />\n面子政治"},{"pid":"48ad80013dc0ee12f61863e725394f99cb314156","tid":2066618,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:42:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">全靠許議員迫班撚樣現真身</span><br />\n班紅官同doj應該 deal 緊邊個攬上身做刀手<br />\n<br />\n所以點解我明知我人檢控難成功都支持所有人做<br />\n因為我講咩分析始終唔係最直接<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">引班死黨棍公開出手干預司法就最好</span>"},{"pid":"571f5ce0c1ea941040c291846651b5ac1091ae31","tid":2066618,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1b8a5ec48281de09e4e8e89d5484386248276dc7","tid":2066618,"uid":76609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T11:42:05.000Z","msg":"整多幾人單私人檢控，<br />\n等佢求其撤到一單就當有做野，<br />\n面子政治"}